# FabManage-Clean - Production Management System

## Architecture
- Frontend: React 18 + TypeScript + Vite + Ant Design
- State: Zustand (slice pattern) + TanStack Query
- Backend: Supabase (Auth, DB, Storage)
- Routing: React Router v7
- Styling: CSS Modules + Ant Design
- Testing: Vitest + Playwright
- Deploy: Docker + Nginx

## Key Patterns
- All modals are right-side Drawers
- Unified tile edit experience
- TypeScript strict mode; interface for props, type for data
- RORO functions; Zod validation; React.memo

## Domains
- Projects & Modules (sequential workflow)
- Tiles (BOM, technical files, CNC integration)
- CNC (machines, queue, utilization)
- Materials (inventory, purchasing, consolidation)

